================================================================================
SECURITY HIGHLIGHTS
================================================================================

FIREWALL RULES (Control Plane):
- 22/tcp    - SSH (restricted to allowed_ssh_cidr)
- 6443/tcp  - Kubernetes API (public via LB)
- 9345/tcp  - RKE2 supervisor (internal network)
- 2379-2380/tcp - etcd (internal only)
- 10250/tcp - Kubelet (internal)
- 10257/tcp - kube-controller-manager (internal)
- 10259/tcp - kube-scheduler (internal)
- 8472/udp  - CNI VXLAN (internal)
- 51820-51821/udp - WireGuard (internal)

FIREWALL RULES (Workers):
- 22/tcp    - SSH (restricted)
- 30000-32767/tcp - NodePort services (optional)
- CNI ports - Same as control plane

ALL INTERNAL TRAFFIC ALLOWED within private network (10.0.0.0/16)

