PENDING TASKS / NEXT STEPS
================================================================================

🔲 TESTING PHASE:
   1. Create terraform.tfvars from example
   2. Set your hcloud_token and ssh_public_key
   3. Update allowed_ssh_cidr with YOUR IP
   4. Run: terraform init
   5. Run: terraform plan
   6. Review plan carefully
   7. Run: terraform apply
   8. Wait 5-10 minutes for cluster initialization
   9. Verify: kubectl get nodes
   10. Test HCCM: kubectl get pods -n kube-system
   11. Test CSI: kubectl get storageclass

